'''''[https://www.instagram.com/gogesportsindia/ GOG ESPORTS]''''' present a BGMI tournament called the ''' Lockdown Warriors Cup  ''' with a prize pool of ₹1,00,000. Phase 1 of the tournament features underdog teams competing for a prize pool of ₹25,000

==About==
===Broadcast Talent===
{{broadcasterCard
|position= Hindi Commentator |lang=en
|b1=Jeet Gaming|b1flag=in|b1name=Jeet Sardar
}}

===Format===
''''' Lockdown Warriors Cup Phase 1:''' 14th August 2021 to 1st September 2021.''

* '''''Round 1:''' 14th August 2021 to 18th August 2021''
** '' A total of 4000 teams will play in Round 1
** '' Teams to be divided into 200 groups''.
** '' Each team will get to play a single match''
** '' Top 2 Teams from each group will qualify for the Round 2''.
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 400 teams}} advance to Round 2.''
* '''''Round 2:''' 22nd August 2021 to 23rd August 2021''
** '' A total of 400 teams will play in Round 2
** '' Teams to be divided into 20 groups''.
** '' Each team will get to play a single match''
** '' Top 2 Teams from each group will qualify for the Semi Finals''.
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 40 teams}} advance to Semi Finals.''
* '''''Semi Finals:''' 24th August 2021 to 25th August 2021''
** '' A total of 40 teams will play in the Semi Finals''
** '' Teams to be divided into 3 groups''.
** '' Each team will get to play a total of 6 matches''
** '' Top 6 Teams from each group will qualify for the Grand Finals''.
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 18 teams}} will advance to Grand Finals.''
* '''''Grand Finals:''' 30th August 2021 to 1st September 2021''
** '' A total of 18 qualified teams will play in the Grand Finals''
** '' Teams will get to play a total of 12 matches in a period of 3 days''
** '' Each day will feature a total of 4 matches''
====Matchdays====
* ''3 Matchdays:  4 Matches Each Day.''
** '''''Map Rotation''''': ''E>>M>>S>>E''

====Allocations====
{{bgcolortext|up|''Top 3}} teams from the overall standings will qualify for [[Lockdown_Warriors_Cup/Phase 2|Phase 2]]

