==About==
===Format===
* '''Group Stage:''''' July 21st - 24th, 2025
** 32 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 30 teams Invited.
*** 2 teams from iQOO Community Cup.
** Teams are divided into 2 groups of 16 teams each.
** Each team plays a total of 10 matches.
**{{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Remaining 24 teams}} advance to ''Semi Finals.

* '''Semi Finals:''''' July 25th - 28th, 2025
** 24 teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8 teams each.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|down|Bottom 16 teams}} are eliminated.

* '''Grand Finals:''''' August 8th - 10th, 2025
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
*** 8 teams from Group Stage.
*** 8 teams from Semi Finals.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
